Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light so glaring that it can't be hidden shatters the silence and revives in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violently quaking and thirsty Earth stakes its life and clashes together with sparks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one more time is enough to create a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power to regain the pages of memory lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs30}The believing heart that penetrates the darkness searches for the place where its soul sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:01:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And burns a sharp glance of eyes that can't sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts of light and shadow head toward the future that the crystal reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they start to move, these eyes brimming red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In my Lost Memory World exists Ancient Egypt from three thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A fierce battle between the High Priests and the Thief Bakura was taking place there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How they each Summoned Monsters to fight was exactly like what Duelists do!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that's true, I'll Summon the Three Illusionary Beasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and Bakura, I'll {\i0}beat{\i1} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mahado's Resolve"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He... forced the God to retreat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't think that he would summon the gods so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I didn't have that gift from Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King, we'll finish this match in the next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there! You're Mahado, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Ring you're strutting out on your chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That belonged to {\i1}me{\i0} originally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'll be taking it back really {\i1}soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let a lowly thief like you touch my Millennium Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so worked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, I'll collect {\i1}all{\i0} of your Millennium Items!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers, give chase!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes, sir!\N - Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see myself out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:04:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you both not see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you see, Pharaoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What exactly is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it related to the Dark Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Pharaoh's godly power...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A {\i0}Ka{\i1} capable of fighting on equal footing with God?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So the Gods are not necessarily the greatest...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh, I'm glad that you are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst Stream of Destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does Bakura have\N the power of Blue-Eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The connection between Blue-Eyes and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Words coming from an occult fanatic like Bakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...hardly catch my attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... those sad cries of Blue-Eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be... stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm well aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Things like fate...\N Things like connections...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't be deceived by false sentiments based off of nonsense not supported by science.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I ever want to come to terms with these illusions...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still no word of Bakura's whereabouts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I have mobilized the soldiers to expand the search area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city around the palace, the desert and even the gorge...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be impossible for him to through a net this wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but Bakura's Diabound has such terrifying power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had the Pharaoh not been able to wield the God...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the power of us priests would not have been enough to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea... Lord Akhenaden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be people living in the city who have {\i1}Ka{\i0} within them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should {\i1}capture{\i0} those people who look promising...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and develop their {\i1}Ka{\i0} to turn them into powerful weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way any commoners wield stronger {\i1}Ka{\i0} than we possess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that terrifying power of Bakura's Diabound...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suppose that power really {\i1}was{\i0} born of his hatred...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You may not know about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:07:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if you place the seven Millennium Items on the stone tablet in the village of Kul Elna...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One can gain the powers \Nof the underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He knows about what happened to the village of Kul Elna...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he really is a survivor from that village, he no doubt harbors massive hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Akhenaden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Bakura, there must be hatred residing in the hearts of thieves and criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a Diabound amongst them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, we might find a {\i1}Ka{\i0} that is even more {\i1}superior{\i0} than the Gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using hatred to create {\i1}Ka{\i0} is such a terrible thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are doing all of this for the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can reduce the\N number of criminals as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this killing two birds with one stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to let the country prosper, I don't mind staining my hands with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that my father, who died on the battlefields, was such a person as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since Bakura appeared, the future is shrouded in shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I must look through this darkness, and prevent the disaster that befalls the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the battle with Bakura, your {\i1}Ba{\i0} was greatly reduced as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recovering your {\i1}Ba{\i0} is also crucial in preparing for the upcoming battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need rest, Isis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kalim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Shada, my Millennium Tauk is the only thing that can foretell Bakura's next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of the Pharaoh and the citizens, I will not rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is the True Door?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More doors appear each time we open one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my watch has stopped moving from when we were in front of the stone tablet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really able to get out from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a very strong feeling about that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only depend on Jounouchi's intuitions at times like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}shittin'{\i0} me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oi~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are traps behind doors as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have said that {\i1}earlier{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how are we going to find the True Door amongst so many doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Yugi is the only one who knows which door it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's the one who's closest to the other Yugi's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you sense anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this place gives me a feeling of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As though his heart has been sealed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this is the loneliness that the other me is feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone here knows who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't recognize any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As Pharaoh, do I really understand them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And do they understand the real me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm pretty sure he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh, how can you be alone in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering what happened yesterday night, please be more cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah no, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana, what a thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand away from the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I heard everything!\N What's {\i1}with{\i0} that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you acting all weird like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Prince are alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should talk to him like how you used to in the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not "Prince"!\N He's "Pharaoh"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know me in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you {\i1}talking{\i0} about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us have {\i1}always{\i0} been together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Learning magic and sparring with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were as close as real siblings!\N We sure had fun together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're really Prince, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something... {\i1}different{\i0} about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Pharaoh now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:13:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The prince is carrying great responsibilities that none of us can understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you called him "Prince", Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry, Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, how did you come here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My magic skills have improved a lot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Binding Spell Technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You fool! Undo that at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan to make the palace defenseless?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The removal spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mahado... Mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At least I exist in their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I do have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The seven Millennium Items...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe it's a little tough\N to get them all at once, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's alright as long as I get all seven Millennium Items in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With that, I will know what the Eighth Key that opens the Door to the Underworld is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If so, I guess I should start by taking the Millennium Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How could you do all this, Bakura...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Holy Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the city going to burn again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let that happen to the city or its civilians again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let the people suffer anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get Master to practice magic with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Priest, Mahado is very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to be more patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Prince", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whoops! I meant "Pharaoh".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana, can you... say my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince is the Prince, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the Pharaoh is the Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Prince is the Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Prince is the Prince... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isis...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:16:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your Millennium Tauk sense Bakura in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your Millennium Ring sense his presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it couldn't sense a single thing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future will smile upon the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It still depicts Bakura's evil intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... A burst of light is piercing through!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, head of the security force, will be heading for Akhenamkhanen's tomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:17:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To conduct a ceremony to reinstate the barrier of the tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are to fail again, your position as Holy Priest will most likely be removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Bakura were to appear, you'd better not take him on alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not someone the likes of you can deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Priest Seto, you speak too recklessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado, please protect my father's tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go, I want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Mahado's student, yet you do not trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he'll be vulnerable when he's setting up the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana, you really don't understand your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado is Egypt's number one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, even if you looked all over the world, you wouldn't be able to find a better wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Shimon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... He sealed off a portion of his powers because he was too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if he were to release all his powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He would most likely be more powerful than any of the other six High Priests.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isis...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't change your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw my future, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything further.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please protect the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so... the one who will emerge victorious... is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mahado!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A-Are you all right, Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mahado!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please don't let this bother you-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hold still.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Prince, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One who will become the Pharaoh doing such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what is the difference between me and you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like how you have red blood flowing through your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I too have the same red blood flowing through mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're the same, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:20:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the future, there will be a world where everyone is equal and living freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I plan to show you it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The new world that the Prince was talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It may be idealistic, but you will surely make it into reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I want to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Valley of Kings\N should be on the left path...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep quiet and continue walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to keep following Lord Mahado!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to defeat his Diabound,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to unleash the entirety of my magical powers... my {\i0}Heka!{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll probably use the forbidden ritual in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:21:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, Bakura! I know that you are following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept your invitation, Mahado.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulling such tricks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To show us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a map isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only what tore apart the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the hope that lies in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without deciding on a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just take a step toward my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.24,0:22:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}EYE'S, while I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.34,0:22:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! EYE'S, if what I wished for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.55,0:23:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...shudders my very soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we were wandering around in the maze of the heart in the Millennium Puzzle,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fierce battle between Priest Mahado and Thief Bakura is taking place in Yugi's Memory World.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado went to challenge Bakura due to his total loyalty towards the Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Bakura's Diabound has become stronger than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Mahado be able to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Battle to the Death! Mahado VS Bakura"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to it!
